Rudy Range Regime v2 — Range Regime Premium Collector for sideways markets. Detects low-volatility, range-bound
conditions using ADX below 25, RSI between 35-65, and Bollinger Band width under 8%. Simulates credit spread entry
during confirmed sideways regimes. Exits after 21-bar hold duration or on 5% protective stop. Includes real-time
dashboard showing ADX, RSI, BB width, historical volatility, and regime mode. Designed for: SPY, QQQ, IWM, XLF, XLE,
MSFT, AAPL, META.
